
---++ Creating an OSG Connect Account

In order to do the following exercise you will need to create an OSG Connect account. To do this please visit http://osgconnect.net/ and select &quot;Sign up as a new user&quot; from the &quot;Sign In/Sign Up&quot; dropdown on the top right of the page. 

You will be presented with an Acceptable Use Policy. Read and accept this policy. 

Follow the directions on this page. Please use your !UserID from the ICTP. I have provided the OSG Connect Support with these IDs to verify your accounts. 

---++ Creating a Jetstream Cloud Account

You will receive an training account and password on paper at the start of the Cloud session. 




